sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant VirtualService as VirtualService<br/>Routing Rules
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>External AuthZ
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EnvoyProxy as Envoy Sidecar<br/>mTLS ISTIO_MUTUAL
    participant REST as REST Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as gRPC Server<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: REST API Call (with Istio)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>VirtualService: Route to model registry service
    VirtualService->>Authorino: Validate request<br/>AuthorizationPolicy CUSTOM action

    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS 6443/TCP
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Token valid (user identity)

    Authorino->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Check GET permission on service/{registry-name}
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Authorized

    Authorino-->>VirtualService: Allow (identity in headers)
    VirtualService->>EnvoyProxy: Forward request<br/>mTLS ISTIO_MUTUAL
    EnvoyProxy->>REST: HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>Validated identity

    REST->>GRPC: Forward to gRPC backend<br/>localhost:9090 gRPC<br/>No encryption (same pod)
    GRPC->>DB: ML Metadata Query<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL Protocol<br/>TLS optional (5432/3306)
    DB-->>GRPC: Query results
    GRPC-->>REST: gRPC response
    REST-->>EnvoyProxy: HTTP response
    EnvoyProxy-->>VirtualService: mTLS response
    VirtualService-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: gRPC API Call (with Istio)

    Client->>Gateway: gRPC Call<br/>Metadata: authorization={token}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (HTTP/2)
    Gateway->>VirtualService: Route to gRPC service
    VirtualService->>Authorino: Validate request

    Authorino->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>Authorino: Authorized

    Authorino-->>VirtualService: Allow
    VirtualService->>EnvoyProxy: Forward gRPC<br/>mTLS ISTIO_MUTUAL
    EnvoyProxy->>GRPC: gRPC 9090/TCP
    GRPC->>DB: ML Metadata Operation<br/>TLS optional
    DB-->>GRPC: Result
    GRPC-->>EnvoyProxy: gRPC response
    EnvoyProxy-->>Gateway: mTLS response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Authorino,K8sAPI: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    participant RBACProxy as Kube-RBAC Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OpMetrics as Operator Manager<br/>/metrics endpoint

    Prometheus->>RBACProxy: GET /metrics<br/>Authorization: Bearer {SA-token}<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>Validate ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Valid token
    RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>Check metrics access
    K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Authorized
    RBACProxy->>OpMetrics: GET /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    OpMetrics-->>RBACProxy: Prometheus metrics
    RBACProxy-->>Prometheus: HTTPS response
